# ── Meta Ads Library ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required by api/meta-token.js to exchange short-lived tokens for long-lived ones.
# Add these in the Vercel dashboard under Settings → Environment Variables.
# For local development with `vercel dev`, create a .env.local file with these values.

META_APP_ID=your_meta_app_id_here
META_APP_SECRET=your_meta_app_secret_here

# How to obtain:
#   1. Go to https://developers.facebook.com/apps/
#   2. Create or open your app → Settings → Basic
#   3. Copy "App ID" and "App Secret"
#   4. Your app needs the "Ads Management Standard Access" permission
#      to query the Ads Archive endpoint.
#
# How to get a user access token to paste in the ACM Horizon UI:
#   1. Go to https://developers.facebook.com/tools/explorer/
#   2. Select your app → Generate Access Token
#   3. Grant permissions: ads_read, business_management
#   4. Copy the token and paste it in ACM Horizon → "Meta Ads Library Token"
#   5. ACM Horizon will automatically exchange it for a 60-day token via /api/meta-token
